For getting a decent pay job postion, people are making an effort on their own way. 
Most people contend that going to a college is the only path to success. Whereas others oppose this idea by saying early work experiences can have an edge over a piece of bachelor degree certificate. This essay will explore both views and state why I believe that going to university is not the only way to fullfill one's dream.


